margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　.inner {</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　width: 200px;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　height: 200px;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　margin-top: -200px;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　}</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　&lt;div class=&quot;outer&quot;&gt;&lt;!--我是透明的容器--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;